tion/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1416%2C945 4x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=403%2C269, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=807%2C539 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1212%2C809 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 425px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?quality=90&amp;resize=403%2C269, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=807%2C539 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?quality=45&amp;resize=1212%2C809 3x\" type=\"image/jpeg\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=553%2C369, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e1575392915182.jpg?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1106%2C738 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 589px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2019/12/CP-005-17-01-18-Robert-Smith-2018_preview-a8cb206-e15753929